original_title: AC/DC: Live at Rijnhallen, Arnhem, Netherlands
overview: AC/DC in Arnhem, Netherlands, on Friday July 13, 1979.  Filmed live for Countdown television series. Setlist includes 1) Highway to Hell, 2) Bad Boy Boogie, 3) The Jack, 4) Rocker, 5) Whole Lotta Rosie
title: AC/DC: Live at Rijnhallen, Arnhem, Netherlands
